```Python
class Solution:
    def numTilings(self, n: int) -> int:
        f = [[0] * 4 for _ in range(n + 10)]
        f[1][0] = f[1][1] = 1
        for i in range(2, n + 1):
            f[i][0] = f[i - 1][1]
            f[i][1] = sum([f[i - 1][j] for j in range(4)])
            f[i][2] = f[i - 1][0] + f[i - 1][3]
            f[i][3] = f[i - 1][0] + f[i - 1][2]
        return f[n][1] % 1000000007
```

* 时间复杂度：$O(n)$
* 空间复杂度：$O(n)$

