* []

```Python
class Solution:
    def numTilings(self, n: int) -> int:
        f = [[0] * 4 for _ in range(2)]
        f[1][0] = f[1][1] = 1
        for i in range(2, n + 1):
            a, b = i & 1, (i - 1) & 1
            f[a][0] = f[b][1]
            f[a][1] = sum([f[b][j] for j in range(4)])
            f[a][2] = f[b][0] + f[b][3]
            f[a][3] = f[b][0] + f[b][2]
        return f[n & 1][1] % 1000000007
```

* 时间复杂度：$O(n)$
* 空间复杂度：$O(1)$

